{"tid":1597590,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔x鳩柒掂喎　C朗近24次罰球全炒","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:48:32.000Z","uid":54373,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f71e2ffda6c953dfa60ec86923e3f5936e208bd","tid":1597590,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">70.8% 唔中龍</span><br />\n<br />\n 意大利傳媒發表意甲數據，其中有一項關於C朗射罰球，結果發現，呢位葡萄牙球王最近24次主射罰球當中，1球都未入過，反而佢嘅祖記隊友比真歷，射6次入1球。<br />\n<br />\n呢項數據係由《Ultimo Uomo》發表，截至前仗對維羅納為止，C朗為祖雲達斯在意甲及歐聯主射24次罰球，<span style=\"color: red;\">結果15球中人牆、2次射斜、7次被門將撲出，入球率係0呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n反而比真歷喺對拿玻里嘅大戰，射入1個罰球。而佢喺2015至18年期間，就入咗11個罰球。"},{"pid":"2ba5659a5d9c6242b2e0fa6bf25359e99a351d6f","tid":1597590,"uid":89037,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"佢目標係省鳩對手然後令對面球員受傷<br />\n唔係入波"},{"pid":"92b3d03dcee21138e44d5e370253a6c72f4925c9","tid":1597590,"uid":51924,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"佢識閪射咩 比真歷好慘"},{"pid":"c3f1de89d6fcaf45deae3c5172a8a22c6b0c3d67","tid":1597590,"uid":52571,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"呢條友冇賓施馬識閪入波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecda0917b5eed9bc1a27d51e1d711d8e139ea54","tid":1597590,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f1de89d6fcaf45deae3c5172a8a22c6b0c3d67","tid":1597590,"uid":52571,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"呢條友冇賓施馬識閪入波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"依個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc20802365eece690fd6a473321b81992ce4b16","tid":1597590,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"你識條鐵！我朗就算射上天都係